Author commentary:

This piece was an entrant in the 2020 Exquisite Corpse contest. Tip o' the hat to my co-author http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/Hinomupi, who supplied the containment procedures. Hinomupi's containment procedures were pretty open-ended, which left me plenty of possible directions to try to take this thing. So I began by focusing first on the reference to  Pieces of Eight, of course, me hearties.

The next requirement that had to be satisfied was the Object Class of  I think I adequately addressed that by means of the discovery that the anomalous effect is triggered only when at least five of the pieces are in proximity- it seems reasonable that this could initially be missed.

This article is, in a sense, a tonal inversion of spikebrennan's proposal. That 001 proposal was intended to start out grim and serious but end up kind of light-hearted and goofy  technology falls into the Foundation's lap, and the Foundation proposes to use it to produce an army of obedient D-class slave-drones.

By  I refer to Joseph Campbell's notion of archetypal characters in a narrative structure.

I intentionally avoided the explicit use of the word  and (2) this thing imposes an archetype - meaning that it doesn't exactly make you talk and act like a pirate, but rather it makes you talk and act like a generic pop-culture archetype of a pirate.

