(1) Image is a re-colored and cropped version of https://www.flickr.com/people/49208525@N08).

(2) Image consist of background image by https://www.flickr.com/photos/36894712@N04 ; with modifications by spikebrennan. I'm a lousy artist, and I'd really like to replace that hand-drawn glyph with a better piece of artwork that combines the Foundation logo with a pirate-style skull-and-crossbones motif. Lemme know if you can help.





